Package: IsoEM
Type: Package
Title: EM-Based Transcript Quantification for Long-Read RNA-seq
Version: 0.3.4
Authors@R: person("hmutpw", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "hmutpw@github.com")
Description: Post-processing package for IsoQuant long-read RNA-seq output.
    Provides a modular pipeline: prepare_isoem() validates input files and
    creates a lightweight IsoEMInput object; build_ec() / build_sc_ec()
    construct equivalence classes from bulk or single-cell data; run_em()
    performs EC-compressed EM quantification; write_isoem() / write_sc_isoem()
    write results to disk. One-step wrappers run_isoem() and run_sc_isoem()
    are also provided. Designed for large files with memory-efficient
    chunk processing and shell-level sort+join.
